<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="no"?><?Xpress productLine="ncc-clause" ?><clause xmlns:xt="urn:xpressauthor:trackchanges" id="_00e2014e-6926-4e6c-82d3-39d789598179" outputclass="ncc-clause"><meta><facet building="Class 1a"/><facet building="Class 1b"/><facet building="Class 4"/><facet building="Class 7a"/><facet building="Class 7b"/><facet building="Class 8"/><facet building="Class 9a"/><facet building="Class 9b"/><facet building="Class 9c"/><facet building="Class 10a"/><facet building="Class 10b"/><facet building="Class 10c"/></meta><sptc>J1V1</sptc><title id="_4e7af516-0d1a-43a1-ac61-faf1255b4ae7">NABERS Energy</title><archive-num>2019: JV1</archive-num><subclause id="_53456653-8547-47b8-a077-f2806bf0480b" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_d98b9402-4623-45c1-b5fe-e7e3c5ef5750">SubClause</title><num>1</num><p>For a Class 5 building, compliance with <xref xmlns:inv="urn:xpressauthor:xpressdocument" format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/3369_4.4.0.xml#_92c4ab2f-48f5-4d14-8cbf-cfeae694a3a8" id="_aacea339-3f68-4220-97fe-65f098cb06ca" inv:access="external" scope="local" type="clause">J1P1</xref> is verified when—</p><ol outputclass="alpha"><li id="_2681624b-2301-4647-b3c0-52f6dbe40aa7">a minimum 6-star <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1375_0.6.0.xml#_ec872d9e-d88d-4372-9d60-43327a3cb139" id="_41d29e83-b589-47e8-a007-eab0dd29ba67" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">NABERS Energy</xref> for Offices base building Commitment Agreement is obtained; and</li><li id="_49e66f8a-39b9-4226-a9c5-ccb4157d4606">the energy model required for (a) demonstrates that the base building’s <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1429_4.0.0.xml#_044c235a-5f51-4bc7-9eb9-7cfba1a0f023" id="_8967bb48-658c-430e-ab8a-782b6617bb6e" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">regulated energy </xref>greenhouse gas emissions are equivalent to at least 6.6-star when excluding—<ol><li>tenant supplementary heating and cooling systems; and</li><li>external lighting; and</li><li><xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1213_1.0.0.xml#_1b0c2237-d3d4-4981-97b8-209936e55520" id="_cc7d95d7-9fc2-4feb-bc76-c3b0f3c5e543" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">carpark</xref> <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1456_25.0.0.xml#_242ba975-4cdf-4b84-9f41-b8d524ee17c2" id="_70f15c86-a4bf-42f3-8733-58709f926502" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">services</xref>; and</li></ol></li><li id="_13169c68-3962-460c-9ab1-ea32922c9ed2">the energy model <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1432_4.0.0.xml#_af6fde9f-147d-4782-8b85-42044e80fd42" id="_777a8b4c-2db5-46bb-acb0-bb40882a4202" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">required</xref> for (a) demonstrates either—<ol><li>a <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1489_0.6.0.xml#_49deeede-a813-43a8-a61d-cfbe54ddb6d8" id="_636d37f2-80e7-41b3-94b3-d331a75e5bcd" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">thermal comfort level</xref> of between a <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1404_0.4.0.xml#_50155542-eddc-47be-acea-a15f2c017dea" id="_ea40d87a-7d48-44c6-a68a-8dbba113c19e" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">Predicted Mean Vote</xref> of -1 to +1 is achieved across not less than 95% of the <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1314_2.10.0.xml#_7da927fe-453e-424f-b6ec-280f4e464397" id="_7d38c3f2-30ff-4e0b-84a0-fd52aff0dc39" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">floor area</xref> of all occupied zones for not less than 98% of the annual <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1341_0.5.0.xml#_22178a20-4ed7-4cee-8507-b36346202638" id="_3be8ba91-758d-497e-86df-5a63b309b456" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">hours of operation</xref> of the building; or</li><li>a dry bulb room temperature is maintained across not less than 95% of the <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1314_2.10.0.xml#_7da927fe-453e-424f-b6ec-280f4e464397" id="_12c173cc-86f1-4d33-ac82-c7fdcf765e8e" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">floor area</xref> of all occupied zones, other than any room containing an indoor <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1487_0.7.0.xml#_4cbd9e00-0622-4dfd-9de4-913c80257732" id="_a68b7624-a6c4-4d8e-ac79-25c82c3b722f" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">swimming pool</xref>, for not less than 95% of the annual <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1341_0.5.0.xml#_22178a20-4ed7-4cee-8507-b36346202638" id="_e808e2a5-7021-403c-a1e6-29cf079406e7" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">hours of operation</xref> between—<ol><li>18°C and 25°C for <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1225_1.8.0.xml#_26276791-20ad-4404-951f-29b5bff0ff80" id="_564b5be8-057c-4b96-b239-8518d5511e19" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">conditioned spaces</xref> with transitory occupancy; and</li><li>21°C and 24°C for all other <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1225_1.8.0.xml#_26276791-20ad-4404-951f-29b5bff0ff80" id="_98e29a5c-e4bf-4a4c-9ea8-0845b746c6d9" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">conditioned spaces</xref>; and</li></ol></li></ol></li><li id="_95e01914-d3bc-4098-adc7-2a5e46499738">the building complies with the additional requirements in <xref xmlns:inv="urn:xpressauthor:xpressdocument" format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/218_0.10.0.xml#_5c3a9a7d-ea69-4d1a-acbf-d8aa23ed15be" id="_5277908a-a058-4a58-adbd-6b6217c18722" inv:access="external" scope="local" type="specification">Specification 33</xref>.</li></ol></subclause><subclause id="_d7082c44-1fc7-4954-9bcb-8aac0bff707a" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_a4f651a3-9210-4e3b-b46a-dcb7e4ae7f9b">SubClause</title><num>2</num><p>For a Class 3 building, compliance with <xref xmlns:inv="urn:xpressauthor:xpressdocument" format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/3369_4.4.0.xml#_92c4ab2f-48f5-4d14-8cbf-cfeae694a3a8" id="_6e009140-21b4-4692-9c89-a78d3bf4d78f" inv:access="external" scope="local" type="clause">J1P1</xref> is verified when— </p><ol outputclass="alpha"><li id="_0ad95f8e-fea1-4aa0-825f-a55b82ad5067">a minimum 4-star <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1375_0.6.0.xml#_ec872d9e-d88d-4372-9d60-43327a3cb139" id="_fb50726a-ca33-4688-9b7a-b6a9b72d24fe" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">NABERS Energy</xref> for Hotels Commitment Agreement is obtained; and</li><li id="_e2c30794-f5b3-4e14-9827-64f4431af718">the operating hours of the <xref xmlns:inv="urn:xpressauthor:xpressdocument" format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1456_25.0.0.xml#_0eac53b3-4b7c-47cc-8a95-b844822d3d21" id="_2558803e-f85b-445d-85da-1d8b1c1bce60" inv:access="external" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="glossterm">services</xref> are not less than 12 hours per day in bedrooms, dining rooms and conference facilities, 24 hours per day in corridors and foyers and 18 hours per day in back-of-house areas; and</li><li id="_f1c2dc26-5ae4-471b-84ef-872b516697d9">the energy model <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1432_4.0.0.xml#_af6fde9f-147d-4782-8b85-42044e80fd42" id="_67b6efb9-93b4-416b-a195-090cbcda504a" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">required</xref> for (a) demonstrates that— <ol><li>the <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1429_4.0.0.xml#_044c235a-5f51-4bc7-9eb9-7cfba1a0f023" id="_00359251-0b0c-41be-b57e-558acdc0759c" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">regulated energy </xref>greenhouse gas emissions are equivalent to at least 5.3-stars; and</li><li id="_b422b465-a892-448f-bd67-3c138153309a">a dry bulb room temperature is maintained across not less than 95% of the <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1314_2.10.0.xml#_7da927fe-453e-424f-b6ec-280f4e464397" id="_d1a7bc87-ea72-450e-99d0-a6cfd34cd8e2" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">floor area</xref> of all occupied zones, other than any room containing an indoor <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1487_0.7.0.xml#_4cbd9e00-0622-4dfd-9de4-913c80257732" id="_4f560fe8-c043-4116-a3a4-ecc0ed983581" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">swimming pool</xref>, for not less than 95% of the annual <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1341_0.5.0.xml#_22178a20-4ed7-4cee-8507-b36346202638" id="_c1b06053-30d6-4c0a-95cd-610f17262790" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">hours of operation</xref> between—<ol><li>18°C and 25°C for <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1225_1.8.0.xml#_26276791-20ad-4404-951f-29b5bff0ff80" id="_db6b19c6-8f4c-4392-9df8-5d07dfe8b32c" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">conditioned spaces</xref> with transitory occupancy and food preparation areas; and</li><li>21°C and 24°C for all other <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1225_1.8.0.xml#_26276791-20ad-4404-951f-29b5bff0ff80" id="_018ba5b0-0615-4d9f-ade5-cf8b4d821cfc" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">conditioned spaces</xref>; and</li></ol></li><li>the space temperature in any indoor <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1487_0.7.0.xml#_fdffe6e3-cc05-474b-9b90-e89a04249c30" id="_9973e609-9b84-46f6-a933-72a9d62a1219" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="glossterm">swimming pool</xref> chamber is maintained at 2°C above the pool temperature during occupied hours of not less than 12 hours per day; and</li></ol></li><li id="_9d4d7515-dca9-47a4-90e8-5bbaf8c97b32">the building complies with the additional requirements in <xref xmlns:inv="urn:xpressauthor:xpressdocument" format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/218_0.10.0.xml#_5c3a9a7d-ea69-4d1a-acbf-d8aa23ed15be" id="_36945c0e-d65c-4b6f-ac76-6fb8235411f7" inv:access="external" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="specification">Specification 33</xref>.</li></ol></subclause><subclause id="_3a21e97a-83c1-46e3-9e41-d6cd52e15736" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_62f775ea-330e-4d23-9434-ffc00a24de8e">SubClause</title><num>3</num><p>For a Class 6 shopping centre, compliance with <xref xmlns:inv="urn:xpressauthor:xpressdocument" format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/3369_4.4.0.xml#_92c4ab2f-48f5-4d14-8cbf-cfeae694a3a8" id="_db330b28-7e4c-4513-a967-9f776e90b913" inv:access="external" scope="local" type="clause">J1P1</xref> is verified when—</p><ol outputclass="alpha"><li id="_f780689a-f271-47e6-9433-adc3f281ef44">a minimum 6-stars <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1375_0.6.0.xml#_ec872d9e-d88d-4372-9d60-43327a3cb139" id="_57e3c0a7-4098-465d-adc2-cd2e5904c284" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">NABERS Energy</xref> for Shopping Centres Commitment Agreement is obtained; and</li><li id="_900f74be-d608-4556-8e5a-7e0adf15cc3d">the building has:<ol><li id="_2f24b41a-4094-4e97-892a-f6e55f603ee2">an <xref xmlns:inv="urn:xpressauthor:xpressdocument" format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1181_1.0.0.xml#_386d327a-f182-4f1a-bf21-5cfdef50cc8d" id="_7fc702bb-41f7-4c23-8128-c9bb872608cb" inv:access="external" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">air-conditioned</xref> common area of not less than 20% of the gross lettable area; and</li><li>a gross lettable area greater than 15 000 m<sup xmlns:inv="urn:xpressauthor:xpressdocument" id="_964790b8-cace-4eee-be45-8299300ae37b" inv:access="external">2</sup>; and</li></ol></li><li id="_baa598d1-9a0f-40d5-a9ed-bbbe68feff78">the energy model <xref xmlns:inv="urn:xpressauthor:xpressdocument" format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1432_4.0.0.xml#_af6fde9f-147d-4782-8b85-42044e80fd42" id="_4b42f38d-aea2-44c7-bd6c-155b1c9ff1ba" inv:access="external" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">required</xref> for (a) demonstrates— <ol><li>the <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1429_4.0.0.xml#_044c235a-5f51-4bc7-9eb9-7cfba1a0f023" id="_2e0660ce-8a26-4a37-8950-d5d11453f475" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">regulated energy </xref>greenhouse gas emissions of the <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1456_25.0.0.xml#_0eac53b3-4b7c-47cc-8a95-b844822d3d21" id="_762acd04-f5dc-41d7-b997-4c5ed1beb416" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="glossterm">services</xref> covered within the scope of <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1375_0.6.0.xml#_e8df48a3-61f5-4510-8ed2-47efe75986d8" id="_3e11c654-9a17-474c-8853-fe550e2a2a53" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="glossterm">NABERS Energy</xref> for Shopping Centres ratings are equivalent to at least 6.7-stars when—<ol><li>excluding carpark services and carpark numbers from <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1375_0.6.0.xml#_ec872d9e-d88d-4372-9d60-43327a3cb139" id="_1972ed14-6f0a-42e0-bcaa-62e919b7948a" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">NABERS Energy</xref> calculation; and</li><li>calculating solar photovoltaic export based on the reduced site energy use arising from (A); and</li></ol></li><li id="_b77dc3e3-d13d-4f4a-81a6-3af459437b5c">a dry bulb room temperature is maintained across not less than 95% of the <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1314_2.10.0.xml#_7da927fe-453e-424f-b6ec-280f4e464397" id="_f4eb5a04-5b3e-44d6-b5c2-dd593f6dbc26" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">floor area</xref> of all occupied zones, other than any room containing an indoor <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1487_0.7.0.xml#_4cbd9e00-0622-4dfd-9de4-913c80257732" id="_513716d5-c46a-4cae-b3cc-87286b5237af" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">swimming pool</xref>, for not less than 95% of the annual <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1341_0.5.0.xml#_22178a20-4ed7-4cee-8507-b36346202638" id="_6281fe14-f689-4103-bedb-f3e1998495e7" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">hours of operation</xref> between—<ol><li>18°C and 25°C for <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1225_1.8.0.xml#_26276791-20ad-4404-951f-29b5bff0ff80" id="_f5c143d3-debf-4253-a101-ac77e5a16e4e" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">conditioned spaces</xref> with transitory occupancy and food preparation areas; and</li><li>21°C and 24°C for all other <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1225_1.8.0.xml#_26276791-20ad-4404-951f-29b5bff0ff80" id="_3529fe39-f332-4193-9038-f6bba4f1a217" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">conditioned spaces</xref>; and</li></ol></li></ol></li><li id="_71b0d374-0863-44e2-8494-f48e837ed9cf">the building complies with the additional requirements in <xref xmlns:inv="urn:xpressauthor:xpressdocument" format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/218_0.10.0.xml#_5c3a9a7d-ea69-4d1a-acbf-d8aa23ed15be" id="_bc7a12cf-8ba5-4fce-baa4-b262f6d2f7f6" inv:access="external" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="specification">Specification 33</xref>.</li></ol></subclause><subclause id="_53c38e7c-4608-454b-b84b-86a8ce14d9de" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_98a1f353-c975-40cf-b1ab-0f17f2c471a9">SubClause</title><num>4</num><p>The calculation method for (1), (2), and (3) must comply with ANSI/ASHRAE Standard 140.</p></subclause></clause>